column100:
Interested in working with street food crepes?  Join the team at  JURA’S PANCAKES  !! 
 We are looking for people who are  
 - service-minded with positive energy  and appreciate customer contact 
 - have a good overview in busy periods 
 - flexible with working hours  
   
 No experience necessary, we will teach you everything you need to know.  
   
 Location Strøget, Copenhagen 
   
 Contact 5040 8295 
 Vi taler også dansk!
